dc_description_s: Plan of the city of New York, in North America, surveyed in the years 1766 & 1767 : to his excellency Sir Henry Moore, Bart., Capitain General & Governour in Chief in and over His Majesty's province of New York ... this plan of the city of New York & its environs ... is most humbly dedicated
